---
import Base from '../layouts/Base.astro';

const tiles = [
  '/images/personal/photo-1.webp',
  '/images/personal/photo-2.webp',
  '/images/personal/photo-3.webp',
  '/images/personal/photo-4.webp',
  '/images/writing/writing-1.webp',
  '/images/writing/writing-2.webp',
  '/images/writing/writing-3.webp',
  '/images/writing/writing-4.webp',
];
---

<Base title="About" activePage="about">
  <div class="about-wrap">
    <div class="about">
      <p>Hi there! My name is Olivia Baker-Sullivan.</p>

      <p>A little more about me: My background is interdisciplinary. I started in visual arts and music, got my Master's in Interdisciplinary Design, and that's really where I shifted from pure aesthetics into systems thinking, research, and strategy. That foundation is still very much how I approach product work today.</p>

      <p>In my early career, I worked across branding and agency environments: Healthcare nonprofits, startups, and then as a designer on the eBay account at an agency, where I built my instinct for designing within established systems and moving fast in cross-functional teams.</p>

      <p>The last few years I was at Block (Square's parent company) I was embedded on a web and product team where marketing and product experience were deeply connected. In practice, that meant all designers bridging web surfaces with in-product journeys, working directly with PMs and engineers on acquisition, onboarding, and global launches.</p>

      <p>Outside of work, I play violin and volunteer with the Strings Attached Orchestra, I volunteer with the RGD on the D&amp;I committee to give back to the design community that gives to me, and I am presently enjoying a combination of hot yoga and Muay Thai for some activity.</p>
    </div>

    <div class="contact-wrap">
      <h2 class="contact-heading">Want to work with me, or just a query? Let me know!</h2>
      <form class="contact-form" action="https://formspree.io/f/xjgppqoe" method="POST">
        <div class="contact-form__row">
          <label for="name">Name</label>
          <input type="text" id="name" name="name" required placeholder="Your name" />
        </div>
        <div class="contact-form__row">
          <label for="email">Email</label>
          <input type="email" id="email" name="email" required placeholder="your@email.com" />
        </div>
        <div class="contact-form__row">
          <label for="message">Message</label>
          <textarea id="message" name="message" required placeholder="What's on your mind?" rows="5"></textarea>
        </div>
        <button type="submit" class="contact-form__submit">Send →</button>
      </form>
    </div>

    <div class="about-tiles">
      {tiles.map((src) => (
        <div class="about-tile">
          <img src={src} alt="" loading="lazy" decoding="async" />
        </div>
      ))}
    </div>
  </div>
</Base>
